{"tid":1615002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(國際策略/對中策略) 入黎討論有咩好計","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:43:00.000Z","uid":143646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c10c1df074deda3987cbfb1bf582d019fbc15ba8","tid":1615002,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"學術性討論 並不代表本人立場 本文其他回覆 責任自負<br />\n在下普通人一名 <br />\n1.講下而家ge<strong>情勢</strong><br />\n10月1 准許用實彈, 係要令示威者激化<br />\n效果:<br />\n(實彈&gt;示威激化&gt;基本法中的&quot;暴亂&quot;&gt;<strong>中央出師有名&gt;各種惡法</strong>)<br />\n<strong>因此要注意:<br />\n激化的壞效果</strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 要有具體行動, 策略 聯合各國 各階層<br />\n單純示威(和平, 激烈)<br />\n對中央比唔到新壓力, 只會借由警察, 控制香港解決<br />\n<br />\n對外國人黎講:<br />\n香港人<strong>爭取緊咩係好模糊</strong>, <br />\n同情亦<strong>唔知道做咩幫到你</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>因此要有具體國際策略/對中策略</strong>,<strong> 只係LIHKG推post只大多流於示威, 需要<ins>**並用**</ins>新策略</strong><br />\n<br />\n3. 對中央黎講, <br />\n香港問題=台灣統一問題<br />\n香港問題=美國貿易問題/ 潛在國際壓力<br />\n香港問題=大陸國家安全問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>現時除左美國搞緊人權法,<br />\n似乎中央冇太大壓力</strong><br />\n<br />\n4.其他問題<br />\n現時靠LIHKG, 上網 分享活動<br />\n<strong>一旦切斷上網,</strong> 示威者自然散去"},{"pid":"7c747fa07b1a868d8333a928eedd71faa75d7901","tid":1615002,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:28.000Z","msg":"冇人理"},{"pid":"22bf4119f2bcfbdcdad1be35cc9bf591b4bd95ef","tid":1615002,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"啲人唔理架，我會覆你。<br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊呢啲嘢"},{"pid":"eb9ce0655ca85fe2879898dab26646b0788f923e","tid":1615002,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:05:38.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dc4e72af5d47f1815a4268e01f9286ab3242a6","tid":1615002,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":